# Stakeholder Analysis - Salesforce PropertyHub

## Primary Stakeholders
- **Sales Agents**: Daily users, need lead management and visit scheduling
- **Property Managers**: Oversight role, need reporting and analytics
- **Prospective Buyers**: End customers, need property matching and communication

## Business Objectives
- Reduce lead response time from 48hrs to 2hrs
- Increase lead conversion rate by 30%
- Improve agent productivity by 25%
- Provide real-time sales visibility to management

## Success Metrics
- Lead response time < 2 hours
- Conversion rate > 15%
- Visit-to-offer ratio > 40%